_sText:
Made by: Wapo and FalO


1 CT spawn
12 Terrorist spawns

The idea is that the 1 CT must shoot all terrorist
before they get to the teleport wich will take them 
to the place where the Terrorists can kill that 1 ct.
 

if you have played the map Kill_the_terrorist, you will understand the idea quickly.
 
IMPORTANT!!!!!!                                                              
you must set mp_autoteambalance 0 and mp_limitteams 0  
otherwise the map doesn't work properly.                           

Have fun playing it.
